---
title: Smart Bacon, Chicken and Roasted Sweet Potato Salad with Maple-Shallot Vinaigrette and Feta
description: As if maple syrup, smoky bacon, juicy chicken, crisp apples and tender, roasted squash weren't enough, shallots do double flavour duty as a tart element and as a base for this balanced vinaigrette. This recipe is a real dinner no-brainer!
